title: NO FEE!! Massive DOT 5Bd, Laundry, 1 Parking Spot, Avail 9-1!!!
posting_body: Landlord paying full rental fee to respective rental agent.
-Huge 1,500sqft 5-bedroom, 1 bathroom apartment located on Roseclair Street in Dorchester.
-Shining hardwood flooring in all bedrooms, hallways and common space.
-Numerous windows including 1 bay window allow for an abundance of natural lighting.
-Countless closets allows for tons of storage space for all tenants!
-Recently renovated kitchen has tiled flooring, microwave, oven/stove, dishwasher, full refrigerator and tons of cabinet space!!!
-Coin-Op laundry located in basement of building
-Cat friendly, and student friendly with co-signer.
-1 parking spot included with the rental of the apartment, everything else is street parking.
-No utilities included in rent, tenant pays for gas, electricity and Wi-Fi/cable.
-Apartment available on 9-1-2022 for a 12 month lease only!!!
-Don't wait, call today before this apartment goes off the market!!!
